PUZZLE ON COINS
suppose there are 10 bags and in each bag it contains 10 coins.
one coin weights 1 gram while in one of ten bags contains the coins which has 1.1grams weight each 10 coins.
Now you need to tell which bag contains the coin with more weight.

ans:
take 1 coin from 1st bag , 2 coins from 2nd bag ,............10 coins from 10th bag 

now by using weight machine you can tell the which bag contains more weight
ex: if bag5 contains more weight coins then 1+2+3+4+5.5+6+7+8+9+10 = 55.5(.5) came from 5th bag .if it is (.2) it is from bag 2

